## Installing ThingsBoard on Raspberry Pi 3 Model B

#### Update Raspberry
```
sudo apt update
```

```
sudo apt upgrade
```

#### ThingsBoard service is running on Java 11. Follow this instructions to install OpenJDK 11
```
sudo apt install openjdk-11-jdk
```

###### below command is needed if multiple java install
```
sudo update-alternatives --config java
```


### Step 2. ThingsBoard service installation
#### Download installation package.
```
wget https://github.com/thingsboard/thingsboard/releases/download/v3.3.1/thingsboard-3.3.1.deb
```

#### Install ThingsBoard as a service
```
sudo dpkg -i thingsboard-3.3.1.deb
```



